{"type": "article", "id": 15467, "title": "带香薰机的柜子", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-24T06:34:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000334QJeyCjBXRI10Gluo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦设计周上还展出了法国设计师 Géraldine Biard 的系列家具“Jardin d’Hiver”，专为失智的人改善生活环境。香薰机里的香气从柜子上立体的雪山山顶发出，白色的可丽耐大理石将柔和的光线透射出来，看到皑皑雪山的图景，令人放松。灯光的明暗是可调的，在夜晚保留一点光，看到自然的图景，能增加安全感。这一系列包括床头柜、书柜和桌案，是柚木板配黄铜的桌腿和把手。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142551eIsPUZznh1Dk6crg.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"603\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73716381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142552iEtoGLWgjdCpfOVR.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"482\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58924205\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142553xqJw6cFpl9UruaSN.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"394\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48166259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}